        "subject": "LU-10938 wbc: Assimilate cache pages in MemFS into Lustre clio",
        "message": "LU-10938 wbc: Assimilate cache pages in MemFS into Lustre clio\n\nWhen WBC EX lock is revoking on a client, it needs to flush the\ncached directories and file data properly.\nWhen flush a regular file under the protection of WBC EX lock,\nit first creates the metadata on MDT and return the instantiated\nlayout. And then, the client needs to acquire all necessary extent\nlocks for file data and assimilate the cache pages in MemFS into\nLustre clio.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nChange-Id: I965d461a50a2746aeac59471e1e40895a5fe4722\nSigned-off-by: Oleg Drokin <green@whamcloud.com>\nSigned-off-by: Qian Yingjin <qian@ddn.com>\n"
